{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_014KfzBkV1af4QSjZxCDPPqs","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a detailed chapter-by-chapter content plan for a graduate-level LaTeX book on category theory. This is a writing coordination task - I should create a team and coordinate specialist writers to produce this comprehensive outline.\n\nLet me think about what's needed:\n1. A writing team lead (me) coordinating\n2. A mathematician/content specialist who knows category theory deeply\n3. Possibly a LaTeX/structure specialist\n\nActually, for this task, I think the most efficient approach is to:\n1. Create a team\n2. Spawn a mathematician writer who can produce a detailed, rigorous chapter outline for category theory\n3. Have them write it to a file\n\n\nI'll focus on bringing in a strong category theory specialist to develop the chapter structure, then have them output a well-organized markdown outline that captures the progression from foundational concepts through advanced topics.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23218,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":23218},"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0748f996-c1ba-4243-9622-0bd6dfd1400e","uuid":"7ea57345-a1b7-49fc-9945-1e8bcb05f5e0"}
